This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as question answering and text classification, which are typically studied in the sub-fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper proposes a unified approach to these tasks using span extraction, which is a common technique in natural language processing. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
